original: Zachrisson, Karl Torbjörn, e. provinsialläkare, Bràlanda, f. 24/12/11 i Fal-kemberg av Axel Zachariais Z. o. Lalla Mathilda Bergiman. G. 38 m. Aina Jenny Eldsäbeth WaHmark. Barn: Björn Einar f. 41, Ulf Göran 42, Sven Gunnar 43, Aina Eva Elisaibeth 46. — ,Stud:ex. i Lund 29, med. kand. där 34, med. lic. v. Karol. inst. 39. E. prov:-läk. i Bràlanda sed. 46.
translated: Zachrisson, Karl Torbjörn, b. provincial physician, Bràlanda, b. 24/12/11 in Falkemberg to Axel Zachariais Z. and Lalla Mathilda Bergiman. Married in 1938 to Aina Jenny Eldsäbeth WaHmark. Children: Björn Einar b. 1941, Ulf Göran b. 1942, Sven Gunnar b. 1943, Aina Eva Elisaibeth b. 1946. — Studied at Lund University, completed high school examination in 1929, medical degree in 1934, medical license at the Karolinska Institute in 1939. Became a provincial physician in Bràlanda in 1946.
